      "global_prompt": "A cinematic Disney-Pixar style 3D animated short scene in a sun-dappled \nautumn park during warm golden hour. The setting features an old weathered \ndark wooden park bench with peeling paint beneath a massive maple tree \nblazing with vibrant orange, amber and yellow leaves, a soft bokeh \nbackground of more autumn foliage with a distant glowing vintage lamppost \non the right. Fallen maple leaves are scattered across the bench and the \nground. Two children are the focus: on the left, a young girl named Lily \nwith voluminous fiery red-orange curly hair, big bright emerald green eyes, \nsoft freckles across her nose and cheeks, fair skin with rosy cheeks, \nwearing a buttercup-yellow floral-patterned sundress with a crisp white \npeter-pan collar and two small white buttons, white canvas sneakers. On \nthe right, a young boy named Max with messy fluffy chestnut-brown hair, \nbright sky-blue eyes, light warm skin with rosy cheeks, wearing blue denim \noveralls with brass buttons and cuffed legs over a red-and-white horizontal \nstriped t-shirt, brown leather sneakers. Painterly textures, rich warm \ncolor palette, expressive cartoon faces with subsurface scattering, soft \ngolden rim light, cinematic shallow depth of field, gentle floating dust \nparticles in the sunbeams.",
      "duration_frames": 281,
