      "timeline_data": "{\"segments\":[{\"id\":\"17790859947990q5qo\",\"start\":0,\"length\":86,\"prompt\":\"Wide two-shot of both children sitting on the weathered wooden bench. \\nLily on the left holds up a small folded piece of old tan paper in her \\nright hand at shoulder height, leaning slightly toward Max with a wide \\njoyful open smile, her bright green eyes sparkling with barely-contained \\nexcitement. Her mouth moves naturally and expressively as she speaks \\nwith breathless wonder. Her fiery red curls bounce gently as she \\ngestures. Max on the right sits calmly with his hands resting on his \\nlap, slowly turning his head a little more toward Lily, his blue eyes \\nsoftening with growing curiosity, a small interested smile forming at \\nthe corner of his mouth. By the end of this segment, Lily's hands begin \\nto lower the paper toward her lap as if about to unfold it. Subtle \\nambient motion in the background: a few autumn leaves drift slowly down \\nthrough the warm golden light, dappled sunlight flickers softly on the \\ncharacters. Static camera, no zoom, intimate medium-wide framing.\",\"type\":\"image\",\"imageFile\":\"f91b2b32eb39fa2792cbbd75a45b32c2cc0459453f25b24ff3fc7d593aab3957.png\",\"imageB64\":\"/view?filename=f91b2b32eb39fa2792cbbd75a45b32c2cc0459453f25b24ff3fc7d593aab3957.png&type=input&subfolder=&Rh-Comfy-Auth=eyJ1c2VySWQiOiJhNjlhNTFjZDZmYzc5M2NjNDlhYzkyNjBiOWRhMjA1NCIsInNpZ25FeHBpcmUiOjE3Nzk2OTAzNTIxNTYsInRzIjoxNzc5MDg1NTUyMTU2LCJzaWduIjoiOGRiMTJhNWUxMThmNzMwMjkzNzA4NjhlMmE2MjA5MWMifQ==&Rh-Identify=a69a51cd6fc793cc49ac9260b9da2054\"},{\"id\":\"1779087031744llp55\",\"start\":86,\"length\":86,\"prompt\":\"The camera focus naturally tightens to a medium close-up. Lily has now \\nunfolded the old tan paper into a full hand-drawn treasure map showing \\na bold red X mark, dotted trails, tiny mountains, trees, and a small \\npirate ship illustration. She holds the map open with both hands between \\nthem, smiling proudly and watching Max's reaction with delighted \\nanticipation, her green eyes glowing. Max on the right reacts with \\nexplosive amazement: his blue eyes go enormously wide in stunned \\ndisbelief, mouth dropping open into a slow awed \\\"whoa\\\" expression, \\nboth of his hands rising up dramatically beside his face in a shocked \\ngesture, fingers spread. His mouth then moves naturally as he speaks \\nwith mounting excitement and growing wonder, hands gesturing \\nexpressively. His messy brown hair shifts and bounces with the sudden \\nanimated movement. Warm sunlight flickers across his astonished face \\nthrough the swaying maple leaves above. Static camera, no zoom, focused \\nemotional close-up, only character animation drives the energy.\",\"type\":\"image\",\"imageFile\":\"d00fd260d74d7f99cd826597becdffe8a9bdfe5fee7ae83dfbbe5bad38a44065.png\",\"imageB64\":\"/view?filename=d00fd260d74d7f99cd826597becdffe8a9bdfe5fee7ae83dfbbe5bad38a44065.png&type=input&subfolder=&Rh-Comfy-Auth=eyJ1c2VySWQiOiJhNjlhNTFjZDZmYzc5M2NjNDlhYzkyNjBiOWRhMjA1NCIsInNpZ25FeHBpcmUiOjE3Nzk2OTEyODk4ODcsInRzIjoxNzc5MDg2NDg5ODg3LCJzaWduIjoiYWQ0NjM4NjZiN2NhZDNiZWM4NWQ1YWJhZjMxZTY2NzgifQ==&Rh-Identify=a69a51cd6fc793cc49ac9260b9da2054\"},{\"id\":\"1779087042866p6voj\",\"start\":172,\"length\":109,\"prompt\":\"The energy bursts forward into joyful motion. Lily springs up from the \\nbench first with overflowing excitement, the folded treasure map now \\nclutched in her right hand raised triumphantly, her left hand reaching \\nout to grab Max's right hand. Max immediately rises with a bright \\nexcited grin, being pulled forward, his free right arm flying up into \\nthe air in pure exhilaration. The two children together rush forward \\ntoward the camera, running side by side past the wooden bench which \\nrecedes behind them, both laughing with wide open joyful smiles. Lily's \\nmouth moves naturally as she speaks with urgent breathless enthusiasm, \\nher words tumbling out with the running motion. Her fiery red curls \\nbounce and fly with the momentum, her yellow dress flutters around her \\nknees. Max's messy hair flies back from the running motion. Autumn \\nleaves explode upward and swirl around their feet as they run, dancing \\nin the warm golden light. The weathered bench and glowing maple tree \\nremain visible behind them in soft focus. Subtle natural camera follow \\nbackward as they approach, dynamic but graceful childlike running \\nmotion, warm cinematic golden hour rim light.\",\"type\":\"image\",\"imageFile\":\"4be6f9b0a4e54d59d7b9aad5847b1746a098cf1cfc1cb7936a3d67545499fd55.png\",\"imageB64\":\"/view?filename=4be6f9b0a4e54d59d7b9aad5847b1746a098cf1cfc1cb7936a3d67545499fd55.png&type=input&subfolder=&Rh-Comfy-Auth=eyJ1c2VySWQiOiJhNjlhNTFjZDZmYzc5M2NjNDlhYzkyNjBiOWRhMjA1NCIsInNpZ25FeHBpcmUiOjE3Nzk2OTEyODk4ODcsInRzIjoxNzc5MDg2NDg5ODg3LCJzaWduIjoiYWQ0NjM4NjZiN2NhZDNiZWM4NWQ1YWJhZjMxZTY2NzgifQ==&Rh-Identify=a69a51cd6fc793cc49ac9260b9da2054\"},{\"id\":\"1779614860601crqul\",\"start\":281,\"length\":79,\"prompt\":\"测试\",\"type\":\"image\",\"imageFile\":\"c73a17e8c575eedcc5204f6913c97d05661b6837382bfb5ae39290aeb4ccafb8.png\",\"imageB64\":\"/view?filename=c73a17e8c575eedcc5204f6913c97d05661b6837382bfb5ae39290aeb4ccafb8.png&type=input&subfolder=&Rh-Comfy-Auth=eyJ1c2VySWQiOiJkNTdlY2Y5Yzg4Yjg2NDY4YjBkMTRmMWIxNzRiM2MzZCIsInNpZ25FeHBpcmUiOjE3ODAyMTI5NzY5OTQsInRzIjoxNzc5NjA4MTc2OTk0LCJzaWduIjoiYzAyY2M5ZDU1YmY3NWIxYjk5ZTkwNjg4ZWEyMjYxNjgifQ==&Rh-Identify=d57ecf9c88b86468b0d14f1b174b3c3d\"},{\"id\":\"17796148676813sa3a\",\"start\":360,\"length\":6,\"prompt\":\"\",\"type\":\"text\"}],\"audioSegments\":[{\"id\":\"1779090630806f2ryi\",\"type\":\"audio\",\"start\":0,\"length\":86,\"trimStart\":0,\"audioDurationFrames\":86,\"audioFile\":\"d968acfb62e1f3d2ef4448bf5ff959b1741844b0c4f8182618cba23bb08b6683.flac\",\"fileName\":\"Lily.flac\",\"waveformPeaks\":[0.07774879038333893,0.09494862705469131,0.09823442995548248,0.17168524861335754,0.18825295567512512,0.23087270557880402,0.251588